  "title": "[Urgent]Brands Associate - No Experience/Office Hours",
  "description": "<p>🔥 LAUNCH YOUR CAREER: TRAINEE ROCKSTAR WANTED! (TRAVEL + LEADERSHIP) 🔥</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>WHO WE ARE</strong></p>\n<p>A globally connected squad that turns fresh talent into industry heroes 🌍. We run campaigns for major brands (think tech giants &amp; cool startups) – and we’re all about <strong>your</strong> glow-up.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>WHY YOU’LL VIBE WITH US</strong></p>\n<p>✅ #NoTwoDaysSame: Work with new brands every few months – from Lifestyle to Corporate!  </p>\n<p>✅ Jet-Setter Perks: Overseas workshops (Aus? China?) + global mentorship ✈️  </p>\n<p>✅ Promo Fast-Track: Go from Trainee → Team Lead in &lt;24 months (no \"paying dues\" for years)  </p>\n<p>✅ Chill &amp; Cheer: Team rooftop BBQs, achievement shoutouts 🎉 + $$ bonuses  </p>\n<p>✅ Zero-Exp Welcome: We teach you everything. Seriously.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>YOUR PLAYGROUND</strong></p>\n<p>🎯 Team up with clients to smash their goals (strategy sessions &gt; spreadsheets)  </p>\n<p>🎯 Rep epic brands at events &amp; campaigns (think pop-ups, digital launches)  </p>\n<p>🎯 Coach teammates &amp; level-up your leadership swag  </p>\n<p>🎯 Help grow our Singapore hub (you’ll help shape our expansion!)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>APPLY IF YOU’RE: </strong></p>\n<p>\"Done with boring internships.\"  </p>\n<p>\"Want my work to actually matter.\"  </p>\n<p>\"Ready to earn stamps in my passport.\"_  </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>**👉 SMASH THAT APPLY BUTTON 👇**  </strong></em></p>",
